rComments: Funny, makes class fun to attend.  He does use the word "uh" a lot, but I just got past it because lectures were so good.  He asks for participatory questions and answers and gets the class involved. Always helpful answering additional questions
Very interesting class. Lots of reading assigned, but you don't have to do all of it to get an A in the class. Really, very interesting.
Not much in the classroom but certainly nice to look at.  Talk about eye candy!!!  Hot Damn!
